    "description": "伟大的事情来了！\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>高达\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>巨大的\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>可爱的东西！\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>202X年\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>与新城镇项目进行中的岛屿的所有通信都将中断。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>派出了一个调查小组对事实进行调查，但他们也失去了联系。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>意识到情况的严重性，政府派出了一支由特种部队组成的第四个调查队。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>然而，运载调查队的运输机坠毁，面临着一个难以处理的巨大真相。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/a29e98f0707eae2a9cacbd828eab1497.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/14e1ab14875be8fa55e5eea738e48772.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/14e1ab14875be8fa55e5eea738e48772.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/14e1ab14875be8fa55e5eea738e48772.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎巨大怪兽<br>拥有多种大小和风格的巨型怪兽登场！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/c2aae43fd073453d1e6384ad87a08c4f.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/18de0298b63ff380943295e6dc321082.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/18de0298b63ff380943295e6dc321082.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/18de0298b63ff380943295e6dc321082.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎战斗系统<br>强有力的四后卫能提供出色的打击感<br>所有元素都适用物理，体现真实战场。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/48839e740ec2101573839c4e52ff20b5.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/916dc5c39e8ec4d210a0ed60c30dec30.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/916dc5c39e8ec4d210a0ed60c30dec30.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/916dc5c39e8ec4d210a0ed60c30dec30.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎辅助任务系统<br>提供袭击秘密基地、镇压巨型怪兽、镇压怪兽群、镇压恐怖分子、修复设施、营救分队长、补给物资、营救分队队员等多种次要任务，<br>每个发球任务都提供不同的完成条件。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/e91fb883c5f8d1fe09362b45a6dd182d.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/3382bb6816c504d07131d5fd561d051c.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/3382bb6816c504d07131d5fd561d051c.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/3382bb6816c504d07131d5fd561d051c.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎战略系统<br>以全岛为背景的世界地图的存在，各种副任务的成功与否改变了岛的状态。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/fb872ab4184e14b1a8864d1ed63154c3.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/527ead329a2257b01507a5c490defa3d.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/527ead329a2257b01507a5c490defa3d.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/527ead329a2257b01507a5c490defa3d.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎病科系统<br>6种兵种根据存在兵种的战斗风格不同<br>根据视野的不同，画面构成也会完全不一样。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/22c84ee57aff45e74b84029d3b0b6064.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/c5119bb404b3e857dc5eef233787d587.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/c5119bb404b3e857dc5eef233787d587.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/c5119bb404b3e857dc5eef233787d587.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎部队系统<br>不是一个人战斗，而是以部队为单位战斗的系统。<br>可以移动，让倒下的我军复活，<br>同样，在倒下时，部队成员也过来让我复活。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/5ac3ae6c03f4040ff03b26843e271015.webp?t=1652157511\" width=350 height=30 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/05746cfe26d8f79b395f085b0de73941.poster.avif?t=1652157511\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/05746cfe26d8f79b395f085b0de73941.webm?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709780/extras/05746cfe26d8f79b395f085b0de73941.mp4?t=1652157511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>◎成长系统<br>部队长和队员们可以利用资源或参加任务成长。",
